<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Adornment Configuration Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>Adornments in a chart can be used to display additional information regarding a data point. Adornments for the points in a chart series can be set by defining <Run FontStyle="Italic" FontWeight="Bold" xml:space="preserve">ChartAdornmentsInfo</Run> for the series; this allows you to specify the appearance and content path for adornments.</Paragraph>
