</Paragraph>
<Paragraph  FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16" TextAlignment="Center">
Fig: <Bold> Adornment Configuration Demo </Bold>
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features:
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Adornments can display information regarding a data point.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Symbols can be set with adornments.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>An adornment can be customized using templates.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features:</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">


<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The check box <Bold>"IsVisible"</Bold> sets the visibility of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"AdornmentsPosition"</Bold> helps to choose the position of DataLabels in the series segment. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"HorizontalAlignment"</Bold> helps to choose the position of DataLabels horizontally. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"VerticalAlignment"</Bold> helps to choose the position of DataLabels vertically. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Symbol"</Bold> helps to choose the symbol for DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"SymbolHeight"</Bold> helps to define the height of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"SymbolWidth"</Bold> helps to define the width of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The color picker <Bold>"Interior"</Bold> helps to visualize the DataLabels' symbol with diffrent color by choosing colors. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Segment Label Content"</Bold> helps to choose the label content of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Segment Label FontFamily"</Bold> helps to choose the font family of label content of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"Label FontSize"</Bold> helps to define the font size of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"FontWeight"</Bold> helps to choose the font weight of label content of DataLabels. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>

